# Dev-only Node static server. It must NOT be deployed: Vercel auto-detects a
# root file that calls .listen() and wraps it as a catch-all serverless
# function, which then serves the ENTIRE site through slow, uncached function
# invocations instead of the static CDN (2s+ per image, blog hangs).
# Excluding it forces pure static serving. Local dev still runs `node server.mjs`.
server.mjs
